Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.05,0:00:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The Master Plan just came in from Army Command.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.51,0:00:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,In the six months following the opening of hostilities, ARUS will focus on defense,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.80,0:00:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,leveraging our national strength and vast territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.60,0:00:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,During that time, we will devote all of ARUS' energies into mass-producing this weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.48,0:00:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That JIOR weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They say it defeated an entire Dorssian fleet all by itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.90,0:00:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We can hold out easily enough for six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.07,0:00:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,To win, we need to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.53,0:00:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Enter your votes now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.37,0:00:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we have confirmation that the JIOR secret weapon has been taken back,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.92,0:00:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,ARUS will enter into an all-out war against Dorssia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.95,0:02:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We will liberate Dorssia. Only through changing its foundation will the world change.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.08,0:02:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You... But aren't you a Dorssian soldier?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.38,0:02:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Factoring in your abilities and the Valvrave, my revolution will come three years earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.14,0:02:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Possess Senator Figaro. Talk with their President, and—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.97,0:02:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?! You're our enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.23,0:02:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You killed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.98,0:02:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Be that as it may, your only option is to choose me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.27,0:02:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll add an incentive, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.32,0:02:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll save this entire school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.94,0:02:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,As well as your girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's no use! It's completely impassable!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You mean we're sealed in here?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Send in some engineers! Hurry!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.62,0:02:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:02:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on! Hang on, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it, cut that out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.96,0:03:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That transmission just now, what—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.63,0:03:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a Sakimori student?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that transmission just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.92,0:03:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, who—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.57,0:03:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.16,0:03:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell anyone about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.91,0:03:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a situation where you can stand on principle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's something you want to protect, get your hands dirty, Haruto Tokishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.05,0:03:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The Valvrave!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.42,0:03:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, right! I can use that to free the stranded ship—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.97,0:03:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.76,0:03:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Your only hope for a future is to make a pact with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.47,0:03:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I know that unless I try?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.52,0:04:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My predictions are effectively prophecies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Have any of them been wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.94,0:04:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I promised myself that I would protect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.45,0:04:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I have to use that curse to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You will make a pact with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,0:04:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're ready, give me this sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding? Give you the peace sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Peace sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.22,0:04:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not on the same wavelength at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.27,0:04:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Senator Figaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.81,0:04:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.19,0:04:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He's an ace who shot down seven fighters in the Andaman Campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.03,0:04:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do this! It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.53,0:04:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Danger is a soldier's business.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.41,0:05:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it! Don't get into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.87,0:05:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A guide program?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That so JIOR-like, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.50,0:05:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's displaying a seriously cute picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.25,0:05:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.17,0:05:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad... Don't touch anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.63,0:05:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That robot is cursed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.85,0:05:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of program is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.16,0:05:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what happened when I used it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.12,0:05:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back! It's not safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.46,0:05:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.84,0:05:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy defensive forces are a single battalion deployed in a flat plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.26,0:05:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We outnumber them 14 to 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Our victory is not in doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.18,0:06:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a matter of victory or defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It is how we win.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.69,0:06:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?! I thought we still had time before the Dorssian fleet got here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.61,0:06:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Those tremors were from cannon fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.74,0:06:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I have it. We'll leave the students behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a high-speed ship standing by at the auxiliary gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.66,0:06:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We will escape, taking only this robot with us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.62,0:06:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right, right. Forget about the students.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.92,0:06:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Work quickly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.13,0:06:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that we would all escape together!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.23,0:06:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We did come here to rescue you, that's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.13,0:06:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But in order of priority, that came second.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.55,0:06:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Kindness and volunteer work are just pastimes to spend extra time and money on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.85,0:06:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Games meant to garner appreciation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.94,0:06:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Senator Figaro... What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.73,0:06:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That we're the ones who get to decide whether or not we'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.99,0:06:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.82,0:07:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying that now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It doesn't work? I have to touch the skin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.50,0:07:10.33,Alt,,0,0,0,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.04,0:07:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Go easy on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.38,0:07:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We're taking him with us as research material.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.76,0:07:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an adult! Aren't you ashamed of yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.09,0:07:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Not in the least. I'm an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.27,0:07:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.64,0:07:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been told that those tremors earlier were from a malfunction in the gravity generator!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.11,0:07:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to get our escape preparations back underway as soon as repairs are complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.19,0:07:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, please wait patiently.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.40,0:07:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lie... That man is lying...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.53,0:07:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do? What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.23,0:08:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... We were fighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.73,0:08:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.02,0:08:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking everywhere for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.56,0:08:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's in the school building.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.94,0:08:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.65,0:08:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The 40th Student Council Petitions Committee is now in session.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,ARUS is lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would they need to lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.39,0:08:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard a military transmission!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.14,0:08:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The ARUS military encrypts their messages
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and then transmits across a wide frequency spectrum using the latest scramble codes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.73,0:08:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You couldn't have heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.65,0:08:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I had help from—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't tell anyone!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.32,0:08:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,From, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.86,0:08:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we adjourn, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.44,0:08:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.44,0:08:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I declare this committee meeting closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.66,0:08:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you have to believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.82,0:08:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm going to put my trust in someone, it's going to be in ARUS.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:09:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gonna run! And leave us behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet they had the nerve to take that robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.21,0:09:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as the Module's gravity generator is repaired, we'll set out immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.96,0:09:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring us evidence, and we'll hear you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.44,0:09:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Sashinami, what are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.23,0:09:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.15,0:09:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoko, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:33.24,Alt,,0,0,0,,Let go! I have to prove myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.78,0:09:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What does taking off your clothes have to do with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.24,0:09:34.49,Alt,,0,0,0,,I don't get that girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:35.82,Alt,,0,0,0,,I want them to believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.24,0:09:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! All right, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.91,0:09:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean it? You said "All right," didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You did, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.17,0:09:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, so please put your clothes on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she some kind of idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.72,0:09:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But it worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.93,0:09:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for all your hard work, ARUS soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.31,0:10:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We all wanted to express our gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Gratitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, our gratitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.86,0:10:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This way! While Takahi has them distracted!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go find proof that those guys are liars.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.41,0:10:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And now... We will sing the school song of JIOR National Sakimori Academy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:28.88,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here in the city great and fair{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:33.34,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}of the rising sun{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.01,0:10:38.18,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}we shine far brighter{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.18,0:10:43.47,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}than the stars.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.89,0:10:48.23,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A new world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.23,0:10:53.57,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and new dreams,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.94,0:10:58.66,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}our ideal is to make them come true one day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:08.79,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Watch over our path, о brightly shining Sakimori.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What the—?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.79,0:11:11.08,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Sakimori"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.42,0:11:21.18,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}echoes throughout the world, "Sakimori Academy."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I love how students are so docile.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is ready, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.76,0:11:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, bring out Haruto Tokishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.34,0:11:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll leave as soon as this song is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.43,0:11:26.27,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}East and West, past and present,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.56,0:11:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.27,0:11:31.44,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it calls out to us to return...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being moved, Haruto Tokishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.65,0:11:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm amazed you knew about these tunnels, Otamaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.65,0:11:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The Miss Sakimori Pageant uses the gym's locker room as their dressing room every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.24,0:11:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, you've been—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.83,0:11:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You damn kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the real thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:12:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.34,0:12:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoko, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They've been holding you prisoner this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't here to rescue me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.90,0:12:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then your phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing! Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.24,0:12:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel so stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.41,0:12:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, thank you for the wonderful song.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.41,0:12:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all, we're ashamed that this is the best we could do to thank the people we owe our lives to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, we'd like—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.09,0:12:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate it, but we're pressed for time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, we insist that you see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry. Please hold that thought for some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Get us out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.18,0:12:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Get us moving, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.77,0:12:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let them fool you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.15,0:12:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody, ARUS plans to abandon us and escape by themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.36,0:13:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They're here to rescue us, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.36,0:13:01.19,Alt,,0,0,0,,No way, we even fed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.65,0:13:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That isn't true, is it, Senator Figaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.37,0:13:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is what he said true?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.41,0:13:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to rescue us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.90,0:13:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,ARUS always does the right thing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.67,0:13:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Senator...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me Moses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.59,0:13:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm about to part this sea of students.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.26,0:13:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.26,0:13:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.02,0:13:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Get inside the school building, everyone! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.60,0:13:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamada-san! Yamada-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.35,0:13:34.98,Alt,,0,0,0,,Crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.52,0:13:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Clear the road! If you don't move, I'll gun you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's shown his true colors, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The Valvrave!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.25,0:13:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.37,0:13:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This belongs to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just a student!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:13:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.22,0:14:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Get down from the transport!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a minute! This is a joke, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.68,0:14:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought. It only works if I make direct contact with the skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. Bit by bit, I'm learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.45,0:14:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up, Satomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all over... We can't take on a whole army.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you were going to stay on top until graduation, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.67,0:14:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like he's your friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.76,0:14:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about these students!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.08,0:14:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and get us out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Please put down your weapons! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.81,0:14:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Others too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.23,0:15:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.23,0:15:02.32,Alt,,0,0,0,,Not so funny now, is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.32,0:15:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hear it for Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We ended up getting saved by Haruto again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.57,0:15:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.58,0:15:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike you, he won't tell you to pay him for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.33,0:15:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never take money from friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.41,0:15:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This means we're safe now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.25,0:15:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.71,0:15:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The situation is no different from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.17,0:15:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.42,0:15:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This Module is already surrounded by Dorssia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How would a second-year know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If the gravity generator malfunction was a lie, what were those tremors afterwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.93,0:15:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.39,0:15:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was a ship running aground, there should have only been one tremor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.48,0:15:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying it was an enemy attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.02,0:15:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Except for this Module, all of JIOR has been occupied by Dorssia. Meaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.86,0:15:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...they've essentially taken your family members hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.07,0:15:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hostage?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.33,0:15:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But Dorssia might do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.33,0:15:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you expect us to do about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's surrender! It's not too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.63,0:16:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,His sign...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.85,0:16:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're telling me to make that pact with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.47,0:16:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Haruto Tokishima you will choose me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.60,0:16:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to end up doing exactly as he says again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.87,0:16:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.75,0:16:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We're surrounded by Dorssia...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.29,0:16:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And we can't trust ARUS.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Let's surrender. We did all we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.93,0:16:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.12,0:16:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is surrendering all we can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.85,0:16:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't fight against Dorssia!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.35,0:16:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't let Dorssia lay one finger on our families!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.86,0:17:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you suggest we do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They have hostages! If they threaten us with them—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.19,0:17:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly! We threaten them back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.74,0:17:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.78,0:17:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We tell them that if they hurt our families, we'll hand this robot over to ARUS!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't fall for blackmail like—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That robot is the key that will change the outcome of the war...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.59,0:17:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.17,0:17:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Use a robot as a hostage?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.22,0:17:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That will work!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.84,0:17:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll work!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.85,0:17:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I never would have thought of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.30,0:17:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. ARUS Senator!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't give you the robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, keep fighting alongside us, just like before!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.69,0:17:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?! As if we would let you manipulate us like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.02,0:17:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, we'll just hand this robot over to Dorssia!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,0:18:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to our two countries continuing as before in their amicable relationship!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.96,0:18:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It means that neither Dorssia nor ARUS can lay a hand on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.88,0:18:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Our families are safe, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And ARUS will stay our ally!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.76,0:18:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That was awesome, Shoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.38,0:18:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.93,0:18:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We're saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.80,0:18:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoko, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.52,0:19:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The path ahead is clear! Waffe squadron, charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.65,0:19:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Valvrave, why aren't you showing yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.65,0:19:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be in such a rush, Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.53,0:19:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant! It's Lieutenant now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.65,0:19:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You saw it on the net, right? It wasn't L-elf piloting it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.14,0:19:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't seen that weapon before!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.72,0:19:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.81,0:20:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.25,0:20:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.67,0:20:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They're damaging their own Module?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.63,0:20:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.22,0:20:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody! Let's stop depending on others!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.76,0:20:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of using anything else as a crutch, let's stand on our own two feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.72,0:20:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We're declaring independence!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.56,0:20:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Make no mistake! Your enemies are back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.49,0:20:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,As of right now, we're independent!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.12,0:21:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Our school is an independent country, an equal of both Dorssia and ARUS!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.62,0:21:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Preposterous! You can't have a country with nothing but children!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.29,0:21:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we form a country?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.29,0:21:07.92,Alt,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.92,0:21:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.09,0:21:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well, let's now take a vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.26,0:21:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Those in favor of independence, please raise your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.43,0:21:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,For it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.43,0:21:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.56,0:21:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Count me in on your crazy idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.64,0:21:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we ought to carefully consider this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.98,0:21:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we have another option?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.46,0:21:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The Module's separating?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.26,0:22:02.93,Alt,,0,0,0,,Yeah, independence!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.26,0:22:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Our own country!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.93,0:22:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm for Shoko's idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:04.69,Alt,,0,0,0,,Independence! Independence!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.69,0:22:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Who in the world is that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.85,0:22:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoko Sashinami!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.51,0:22:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The daughter of JIOR's prime minister!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.27,0:22:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Independence! Independence!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.66,0:22:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this strange sensation?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.66,0:22:31.96,Alt,,0,0,0,,Independence! Independence!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.00,0:22:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't laughed in a long, long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.52,0:24:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, episode 5, Singing Sakimori Academy".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.40,0:24:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Valvrave... The system that will expose the truth of the world.
